# <p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">This custom transformer uses a look-up table with the url of each resources where the list attribute language{} contains the value 'fr' and change the value of resources{}.language to 'en-fr' for Alberta province in the P/T project of the FGP.</p>
